{"tid":2410961,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"54歲黎明帶愛女出海避疫 傳與助手Wing牛年「追仔」｜望打破「四大外父」宿命","createTime":"2021-02-17T04:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T07:05:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f8b1aa0ebc3befeafc36d1d582acd3e5c3761f","tid":2410961,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"18年，失婚女助手陳泳儀（Wing）為黎明誕下女兒，榮升爸爸的Leon自此便湊女為樂，加上近年受疫情影響，工作量大減的Leon，幾乎將所有時間畀晒囡囡，甚少以「明福俠」形象現身網上，一家三口過得好快樂。<br />\n<br />\n未有疫情前，Leon會與Wing及囡囡飛到外地享受假期，疫情關係，無得外遊下只好留在香港，今日有周刊影到Leon與Wing一家人出海玩，又指35歲的Wing已調理好身體，準備為Leon追番個「牛仔」，希望為他打破四大天王的「四大外父」宿命。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_776404_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_776404_0&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=06fa1531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_776404_0&h=b80748cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_776404_0</a>"},{"pid":"606eda5ae08bdc68f5ee2ba2a9ec84809eff3e75","tid":2410961,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"完全唔知佢生左女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9a2271d389cc906dba37b12655f1b942229930","tid":2410961,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606eda5ae08bdc68f5ee2ba2a9ec84809eff3e75","tid":2410961,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"完全唔知佢生左女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"生左好耐啦"},{"pid":"15277921ef81358ad06304a7fe646757013d8750","tid":2410961,"uid":27616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"失婚女助手？<br />\n即係黎明都要幫人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}